snippet: Local election results showed the main opposition party winning nine of 17 races for big-city mayors and provincial governors, and candidates from the governing party won the remaining eight races.
lead_paragraph: Local election results showed the main opposition party winning nine of 17 races for big-city mayors and provincial governors, and candidates from the governing party won the remaining eight races.

headline.main: In South Korean Voting, No Clear-Cut Victory for Either Party
headline.print_headline: In South Korean Voting, No Clear-Cut Victory for Either Party
